{"tid":1005363,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【出軌代價】吳秀波上大陸節目整個人被P走「國民大叔」慘變「馬賽克」","createTime":"2019-02-02T07:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T13:11:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b41c077923c386844e290a6996e9478460efb420","tid":1005363,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"一段不倫戀，令大陸「國民大叔」吳秀波身敗名裂！50歲的吳秀波去年9月遭比他年輕25年的女星陳昱霖踢爆有婚外情，有指女方要求天價掩口費，吳秀波為求「甩身」，疑引情婦回國，設局逮捕她，令形象跌入谷底。<br />\n近年大陸官方對藝人品德很注重，會將劣跡藝人封殺。而吳秀波在出事前已錄製完畢的浙江衛視《王牌對王牌》昨晚播出，竟然完全不見他的蹤影。有網民將節目播出畫面與現場錄影流出的側拍照作比對，發現吳秀波原本站在黃渤旁邊，但節目出街只見到馬賽克的痕跡，推測製作組已將吳秀波「P」走了。<br />\n日前有疑似該節目剪輯師在朋友圈發文：「P了三天三夜應該是不仔細找都看不出來了&hellip;&hellip;怎麼剛入職就碰上這種事，唉，我盡力了。」<br />\n50歲吳秀波爆發出軌風波後，引發一連串後續效應，包括新片《情聖2》撤檔、舊劇重播時片尾演員表除名，如今連錄好的節目也遭殃，未來更可能被影視公司及廣告商追討賠償，估計最少損失超過十億元人民幣，看來波叔還有排頭痛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190202/large/1549082416_0062.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190202%2Flarge%2F1549082416_0062.jpg&h=770366d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190202/large/1549082445_2ed1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190202%2Flarge%2F1549082445_2ed1.jpg&h=9b10fead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190202/large/1549082445_09ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190202%2Flarge%2F1549082445_09ee.jpg&h=a643c8d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"187e22ae465559000a2c0378fbc8d2ece421fc0c","tid":1005363,"uid":160701,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"魔術show"},{"pid":"685c7702ad21ef02dbcf102a408fffd96e411ee1","tid":1005363,"uid":171598,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"P圖個條油 可以直接過荷里活開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0500d88b086b158e10a639f05b263d15e60bd2","tid":1005363,"uid":20074,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"平時特技假到<br />\n呢d維穩野就技術一流"},{"pid":"ea404c583a4bcb2c2c195c5c21a3fe744cb230ed","tid":1005363,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:26:26.000Z","msg":"司馬懿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fa15e9d3f466ef847736eab7c3361d3f18901f","tid":1005363,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"道德大國！"},{"pid":"6ba2ead2c91fa2ffe3953b097e398814f45fda43","tid":1005363,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"685c7702ad21ef02dbcf102a408fffd96e411ee1","tid":1005363,"uid":171598,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"P圖個條油 可以直接過荷里活開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3802f545879e010f257d0193b9d495a77e214a5a","tid":1005363,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C9WbNPbs-K0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC9WbNPbs-K0&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2WINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=8633e7b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C9WbNPbs-K0</a><br />\n蕭生又中,一早講條友無得撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0219b620f590a42b689063329a5436f995cf8